! Work in progress


! Use GNU make for builds


> Make binary

  make


> CORSIS compilation flags (case-sensitive)

  FLAG			DEFAULT? / DESCRIPTION
  
  static		- link libc statically
  llvm			+ force clang as C compiler (default, except on MIPS)
  gcc                   - force gcc   as C compiler (default on MIPS)
  portable-loops	- do not use splice(2) on Linux
  portable-threads	- do not use POSIX threads (not implemented)

  > Examples

    f=llvm   make
    f=gcc    make
    f=static make

    f="static portable-loops" make
    f="gcc    portable-loops" make

    f="llvm static portable-loops portable-threads" make

  # Time builds with LLVM vs GCC

    time f=llvm make
    time f=gcc  make    


> Clean up

  make clean
